There was a slight chortle from MACH KICK as he leaped on board. While
TUSCON is larger than MACH KICK, the disparity was not so large that
he could literally ride on his head, but he could get on his back
without too much trouble.

(OOC: Don&#39;t forget Tuscon is only about 10&#39; tall/long or so, not
counting tail, Mach Kick is about 6 or 7. Beastmodes do not size
change)

BIG CONVOY just stares at the ceiling. Anyone who follows his stare
can see some reinforced buttressing that goes along the top. &quot;If you
were the jailers, where would you hide your electrical conduit?&quot; He
said quietly, as he directed his chin towards the cieling which was
approximately 20 feet in the air. &quot;Behind as much armor as you could
put in place.&quot;

There was a low whisper from BREAK, &quot;Yeah, it won&#39;t be easy to get at
it, especially with the guards looking.&quot;

BREAK was of course talking about the trio of sharkticon looking
gaurds still standing there watching with keen interest MACH KICK
riding on TUSCON&#39;s back from the other side of the energized bars. So
far they made no effort to do anything about it their antics yet.

&quot;That is some strange training you have!&quot; They said as one of them
folded his arms over his chest. &quot;I don&#39;t think it&#39;s going to help in
the games. &quot;

